---
title: Sri Lankan Chicken Curry with Broccolini & Basmati Rice
description: This creamy coconut chicken curry will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night. It's filled to the brim with bright veggies and finished with a sprinkling of flair from the coriander.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sri-lankan-chicken-curry-ad669344.jpg
